In Sprint 4, each team member was assigned a specific task bundle.
Henry was responsible for sprint planning, submission preparation, final integration, and movement cleanup.

Aaron was responsible for Bundle A: Menu + Pause Flow, including the implementation of the main menu, gameplay flow, and pause flow.

Isaac was responsible for Bundle B: HUD + Score / Strawberry UI, including the HUD and player-facing interface elements such as score and strawberry count.

Zijun was responsible for Bundle C: Strawberry Collection Polish, including polishing strawberry collection behavior, collection feedback, reset behavior after death, and related visual/audio responses. This work also included fixing a previous bug and adding a text prompt for collection feedback.

