Strawberry collection #21 request by Zijun Lu   reviewed by Henry
Strengths:
This pull request successfully improved the strawberry collection polish by adding both sound and feedback-related features. A major strength of this work is the implementation of sound effects for Madeline’s actions and movement, 
including different footstep sounds on different surfaces, which makes gameplay feedback more immersive and responsive. Another strength is the asset integration approach: instead of importing sound effect files one by one manually, 
the implementation used the XML to organize and load sound assets more efficiently.                                                                                                                            
Technical Concerns / Suggestions:
The implementation is strong overall, but there are a few areas that could be improved in future iterations. Some sound effects may need additional volume balancing so that certain clips do not overpower others during gameplay.
